      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 1. Entry Point       — Receives chat message\n## 2. Load State        — Creates or loads session by sessionId\n## 3. AI Agent1         — Detects intent & extracts property filters\n## 4. Output Schema     — Enforces structured JSON output\n## 5. LLM1              — Powers AI Agent1\n## 6. Check Row         — Checks if sessionId exists in DataTable\n## 7. Session Gate      — Exists → Switch | New → Insert row\n## 8. Insert Row        — Creates empty session row in DataTable\n## 9. Action Router     — search_db → Property | get_weather → Weather | general_chat → Chat\n## 10. HTTP Request     — Calls WeatherAPI with extracted location\n## 11. Weather Agent    — Formats weather into readable response\n## 12. LLM Weather      — Powers Weather Agent\n## 13. Clean Filters    — Strips empty / null / zero from updatedState\n## 14. Save State       — Updates DataTable row with new filter values\n## 15. Property Agent   — Validates fields → queries Supabase → formats listings\n## 16. LLM Property     — Powers Property Agent\n## 17. Supabase         — Fetches top 3 matching properties\n## 18. Chat Agent       — Handles greetings & guides user to property search\n## 19. LLM Chat         — Powers Chat Agent",
